OL,3,CBeatrice and Eugenie to skip Royal
OL,4,CFamily's Easter Sunday church outing
OL,6,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor's daughters
OL,7,FPrincess Beatrice and Princess Eugenie
OL,8,Fwill not join the Royal Family for
OL,9,Ftheir traditional Easter church
OL,10,Fservice this Sunday.
OL,12,FWith the agreement of the King,
OL,13,FBeatrice and Eugenie have made
OL,14,Falternative plans and will miss the
OL,15,Ftraditional royal gathering at Windsor
OL,16,FCastle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
