OL,3,CBeatrice and Eugenie to skip Royal
OL,4,CFamily's Easter Sunday church outing
OL,6,FThe decision comes after the former
OL,7,FDuke of York's arrest on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmisconduct in public office and the
OL,9,Fscandal surrounding his friendship
OL,10,Fwith paedophile Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,12,FBeatrice and Eugenie, who are the
OL,13,FKing's nieces, joined the Royal Family
OL,14,Ffor Christmas at Sandringham in
OL,15,FDecember.
OL,17,FIt is understood they will be at
OL,18,Ffamily celebrations in the future.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
