OL,3,CBeatrice and Eugenie to skip Royal
OL,4,CFamily's Easter Sunday church outing
OL,6,FThe King, the Queen and other members
OL,7,Fof the family are set to attend the
OL,8,FEaster Matins church service at St
OL,9,FGeorge's Chapel, Windsor Castle, as
OL,10,Fthey traditionally do each year.
OL,12,FAmong those expected to attend are the
OL,13,FPrince and Princess of Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
