OL,3,CBeatrice and Eugenie to skip Royal
OL,4,CFamily's Easter Sunday church outing
OL,6,FBeatrice and Eugenie, who are
OL,7,Fgranddaughters of the late Queen
OL,8,FElizabeth II, have faced scrutiny
OL,9,Fthemselves after their names appeared
OL,10,Fin the document dump relating to the
OL,11,Fconvicted sex offender recently
OL,12,Freleased by the US Department of
OL,13,FJustice.
OL,15,FOne email exchange suggested their
OL,16,Fmother, Sarah Ferguson, took her
OL,17,Fdaughters to see Epstein in the US
OL,18,Fjust days after he was released from
OL,19,Fprison for child sex crimes.
OL,21,FThey were 19 and 20 at the time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
