OL,3,CBeatrice and Eugenie to skip Royal
OL,4,CFamily's Easter Sunday church outing
OL,6,FSarah meanwhile lost her Freedom of
OL,7,Fthe City of York title last week after
OL,8,Fcouncillors voted unanimously to
OL,9,Fremove the honour over her links to
OL,10,FEpstein.
OL,12,FEugenie was reported to have stepped
OL,13,Fdown as patron of charity Anti-Slavery
OL,14,FInternational in March, a role she has
OL,15,Fheld for seven years.
OL,17,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,18,Fweekly podcast about the royal family,
OL,19,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,20,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson...
